OL,3,CCalls for older Channel Islands'
OL,4,Cdrivers to have compulsory eye tests
OL,6,FThere are calls for Guernsey and
OL,7,FJersey to follow the UK's lead and
OL,8,Fintroduce compulsory eyesight tests
OL,9,Ffor drivers over 70.
OL,11,FIt comes after UK politicians are
OL,12,Fconsidering an overhaul of road safety
OL,13,Flaws there.
OL,15,FThe reported proposals include
OL,16,Fintroducing mandatory eye tests every
OL,17,Fthree years for motorists over the age
OL,18,Fof 70, with people banned from driving
OL,19,Fif they fail.
