OL,3,CCalls for older Channel Islands'
OL,4,Cdrivers to have compulsory eye tests
OL,6,FIn Jersey last year, there were 409
OL,7,Frecorded vehicle collisions - of those
OL,8,Fdrivers, 12% were aged over 70.
OL,10,FOptometrist Jacqui Ryan believes all
OL,11,Fpeople should have regular eye tests,
OL,12,Fbut adds that the likelihood of
OL,13,Fdeveloping conditions like glaucoma
OL,14,Fand cataracts increases as someone
OL,15,Fgets older.
OL,17,FShe says annual eye examinations after
OL,18,F70 should be part of a person's
OL,19,Froutine health check, not just their
OL,20,Fdriving license applications.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
