OL,3,CCalls for older Channel Islands'
OL,4,Cdrivers to have compulsory eye tests
OL,6,F"We're not here to take your license
OL,7,Ffrom you, we're here to help you make
OL,8,Fthe most of your vision and keep you
OL,9,Fon the road as long as we possibly
OL,10,Fcan, safely."
OL,12,FOthers have their reservations,
OL,13,Fhowever.
OL,15,FDavid Inglis from Age Concern says he
OL,16,Ffeels legislation is unnecessary, with
OL,17,Fmany people carrying out routine eye
OL,18,Fchecks from this age anyway.
