OL,3,CCalls for older Channel Islands'
OL,4,Cdrivers to have compulsory eye tests
OL,6,FHe says we should trust people to know
OL,7,Fwhen they are concerned about their
OL,8,Feyesight, as this is "is something
OL,9,Fthat they have to experience for
OL,10,Fthemselves".
OL,12,FDavid adds: "People rely on their
OL,13,Fcars, and that is so important for
OL,14,Fthem in terms of their independence.
OL,16,F"They don't want to rely on family
OL,17,Fmembers just to do their shopping,
OL,18,Fthey want to do it themselves - so
OL,19,Fwe've got to ensure they get access as
OL,20,Fand when they need it."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
