OL,4,Cdrivers to have compulsory eye tests
OL,6,FJersey's Driver and Vehicle Standards
OL,7,Fsay they will also "review the details
OL,8,Fof the UK's new Road Safety Strategy
OL,9,Fonce it is published", and aim to
OL,10,F"align with national best practices".
OL,12,FThey add that "any changes to local
OL,13,Flicensing requirements will be subject
OL,14,Fto careful local consideration",
OL,15,Fincluding consultation with relevant
OL,16,Fstakeholders.
